    
    * Correct ttyACM0 port configuration *

Port config:

    sudo stty -F /dev/ttyACM0 115200 raw -echo -ixon -ixoff min 0 time 1

Then manually send with printf:

    printf "led2 off\n" | sudo tee /dev/ttyACM0 > /dev/null

Or even simpler:

    printf "fan on\n" > /dev/ttyACM0

Or interactively with screen:

    sudo screen /dev/ttyACM0 115200

To go out from screen:

    CTRL^A then next 'k' and 'y'
